{
  "stem": "9898.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I went from Kutno to see them in Wloclawek, and that's the last time, in 1939, that I saw my parents and my sister.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- oh, I remember the night of September 18 or 19.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were surrounded by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How did we know?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because there were fires all over around us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So September 19, we surrendered.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, we had-- I never forget this-- we had fantastic revolvers, and the Germans were after this.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the first thing when we came out, they ask if there are revolvers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we buried all the revolvers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they took us in a big transport to-- by train-- to city of Lodz in Poland.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, there was a big hospital for POWs, and I was working in the hospital for the POWs from September until March 1940.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In March 1940, they send us, the group of physician, to a small town near Posen in Pomerania.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The name of it was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Again there, there was a big hospital for the POWs, and I was working there [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] until June 1940.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Something peculiar happened there in June 1940.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "According to the Geneva Convention, all the physician which are not needed for the treatment of the POWs should have been discharged.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they let us go, 11 of us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I remember the chief doctor was an officer from the First World War, a doctor, too.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was telling me, as long as you can stay with us, which the military do, because when you go out, you will be under the SS and the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was a German military--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The German-- yeah, German military man, very nice guy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I even have a document signed by him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now-- That's it.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
